ke Us One, </div><div class="t m275 xa9 h15 y268 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a multi-</div><div class="t m776 xaf h15 y34f ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">authored, round-table discussion </div><div class="t m2f6 xaf h15 y1313 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of cultural diversity in the </div><div class="t m1330 xaf h15 ybf ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">church, addresses the global </div><div class="t m1169 xaf h15 y1d2d ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mission of Seventh-day </div><div class="t ma22 xaf h15 y1a71 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Adventism and challenges its </div><div class="t me0d x2b h15 y147c ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">members to remove racial bar-</div><div class="t mb54 x2b h15 y1794 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">riers and build bridges of under-</div><div class="t m86a x14 h15 y1460 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">standing as the cross of Christ demands. </div><div class="t m1199 x36 h15 y19f9 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This unique work provides a blueprint and a challenge for </div><div class="t md0f x14 h15 yd15 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christians to love each other and reflect the image of God in </div><div class="t m1648 x14 h15 y2ac ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the last days. </div><div class="t m3f x14 h9 y14b2 ff1 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">US$ 12.95/Ccin$ 18.80. Paper. </div><div class="t ma19 x14 h15 y992 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Available now at your local ABC, or call toll free </div><div class="t m81e x5d h9 y11ff ff1 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1-800-765-6955. </div><div class="t m2817 x14 h34 ye16 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">©1995 Pacific Press Publishing Association 935/59591 </div><div class="t m7bc x61 h15 y240c ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
